The paper proposes a new method for updating a Pareto archive in multiobjective optimization problems. This is a common problem in many areas of computer science, including artificial intelligence, optimization, and robotics. The paper also experiments with different benchmarks and applies the method to a specific problem, the traveling salesperson problem. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms), cs.LG (Machine Learning), and cs.RO (Robotics).
